{"word":"G2564 - καλέω - kaléō - kal-eh'-o - Bid","slug":"G2564","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kaléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kal-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - kaleo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kal-eh'-o</i><p/>Akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G2753\">G2753</a>; to &ldquo;call&rdquo; (properly aloud, but used in a variety of applications, directly or otherwise): - bid, call (forth), (whose, whose sur-) name (was [called])."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479\">G479</a>"}]}